---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About" 
  description="Learn more about Project Meridian Blog"
>
  <section class="container py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Project Meridian</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg">
        <p class="lead">
          Welcome to Project Meridian Blog, a platform dedicated to sharing insights, 
          updates, and innovative ideas that shape our future.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          At Project Meridian, we believe in the power of knowledge sharing and 
          collaborative innovation. Our blog serves as a hub for thought leadership, 
          technical insights, and forward-thinking perspectives.
        </p>
        
        <h2>What We Cover</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Technology trends and innovations</li>
          <li>Industry insights and analysis</li>
          <li>Best practices and methodologies</li>
          <li>Case studies and success stories</li>
          <li>Future-focused perspectives</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Contributing</h2>
        <p>
          We welcome contributions from thought leaders, innovators, and experts 
          in various fields. If you're interested in sharing your insights with 
          our community, please reach out to learn more about our contribution 
          guidelines.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Stay Connected</h2>
        <p>
          Subscribe to our <a href="/rss.xml">RSS feed</a> to stay updated with 
          the latest articles and insights from Project Meridian.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>